                   <script type="text/javascript">
                    $(function () {

        table.append($("<img />").attr("src", "/images/ajax-loader.gif").attr("alt", "News loading..."));

        $.get("https://www.santamonica.gov/api/PressReleases/Recent/6", function (result) {
            var items = result || new Array();

            var rows = $.map(items, function (e, i) {
                return newRow(e).addClass(i % 2 == 0 ? "" : "altItem").get();
            });

            table.empty();
            table.append(rows);
        });

        function newRow(item) {
            return $("<tr />").append(newCell(item));
        }

        function newCell(item) {
            return $("<td />").attr("valign", "top").append(newLink(item));
        }

        function newLink(item) {
            return $("<a />").attr("href", item.Url).addClass("newsItemLink").text(item.Title);
        }
    });
